Package adrenaline.client

Interface ConnectionHandler

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    RMIHandler, SocketHandler
    public interface ConnectionHandler
    The ConnectionHandler interface,The RMIHandler and SocketHandler will implements it. send message from client to server,and received the return value.
